name: Dream not
description: A lovely day, a happy song, a dream so far and distant... Go back and work, this is your way, no matter how you want it. Make steady steps, climb up the hill, look happy way is there hanging... step back for now, it's not your place, go home go write your homework. Amazing stuff, I love this day, You gonna win that lottery... Take this delay, don't cry today, just take you shit and keep it. ||||  Pastels on pressboard, 100x70
